{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The entire world has declared war against <strong>God</strong>. In response, <strong>God </strong>has declared war against the entire world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In other words, <strong>it's time for that fucking crusade.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VERSEBREAK</strong> is a fast-paced ultraviolent elemental FPS set in a unique world where the entirety of history has been re-written. Rip your way through augmented humans, monsters, and demons to tear apart an evil cult that controls the entire world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920290/extras/leSwords.gif?t=1735718644\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABILITIES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use melee weapons and the <strong>four elements</strong> in unique ways to brutally kill enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine abilities together to form even stronger abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MANIPULATE </strong>abilities mid-flight to make them more powerful and gain fine control over their movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill enemies in <strong>complex </strong>or <strong>stylish </strong>ways to temporarily increase your brain power, granting access to even more powerful abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heal by <strong>taking damage</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920290/extras/bloodsword.gif?t=1735718644\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MOVEMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move freely in any direction, both inside and outside of combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Avoid enemies by soaring above them with <strong>Flame Propulsion</strong>, or quickly evade attacks by <strong>Dashing</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the four elements for additional unique movement abilities as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VERSEBREAK</strong> has a detailed multi-layered story set in a dark fantasy world where the entirety of planet Earth got Isekai'd. The story is told through dialogue, hidden books, and environmental storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920290/extras/leShatter.gif?t=1735718644\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2920290?t=1735718644","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2920290?t=1735718644","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920290/8aff94993dae31f2479b4d209c83ef9c8a996fd8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735718644","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920290/8aff94993dae31f2479b4d209c83ef9c8a996fd8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735718644","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Blood and Gore, Intense Violence"},"demos":[{"appid":3259630,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The entire world has declared war against <strong>God</strong>. In response, <strong>God </strong>has declared war against the entire world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In other words, <strong>it's time for that fucking crusade.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VERSEBREAK</strong> is a fast-paced ultraviolent elemental FPS set in a unique world where the entirety of